author: Zach Taylor
title: Texans Trounced By Falcons
text:
Home » Sports » Texans Trounced By Falcons Texans Trounced By Falcons Posted by Zach Taylor Sports Monday, October 5th, 2015 
ATLANTA (AP) _ Devonta Freeman scored three more touchdowns as the Atlanta Falcons romped to a 48-21 victory over the hapless Houston Texans on Sunday. Freeman has scored six TDs in the last two games. The Falcons improved to 4-0 for only the fourth time in franchise history. Freeman had touchdown runs of 16, 23 and 6 yards.
